      • subscribe

        public abstract void subscribe(NodeInfo forNode,
                               java.util.function.Consumer<Notification> notificationConsumer)
        Subscribe ot incoming norifications. Old subscriber must be discarded. New consumer should receive notifications received from the moment it is registered. The method must not block.
        Parameters:
        forNode - node to which receive notifications
        notificationConsumer - the consumer that process incoming notifications in non-blocking manner, e.g. it should return without waiting
